  "prompt": "Where can I learn Tai-Chi in Bangalore?",
  "response": "There are several places in Bangalore where you can learn Tai Chi. Here are a few options you can consider:\n\n1. **Tai Chi Academy Bangalore**: They offer classes and workshops in Tai Chi and Qi Gong. You can join their regular classes or sign up for a workshop to get started.\n\n2. **Nightingale Wellness**: Nightingale Wellness provides Tai Chi classes along with other holistic health practices. They focus on teaching Tai Chi for health and relaxation.\n\n3. **Total Yoga**: Although primarily known for yoga, some branches may offer Tai Chi sessions or workshops. Inquire with them about any upcoming Tai Chi events.\n\n4. **Yogi Re**: This wellness center offers various forms of movement therapy, including Tai Chi. They provide personalized sessions and group classes.\n\n5. **Local Community Centers**: Check out local community centers or clubs as they might have Tai Chi classes. Places like Bangalore Club, Koramangala Club, and others may offer such activities.\n\n6. **Online Platforms**: If you prefer learning from home, there are plenty of online platforms offering Tai Chi classes. Websites like Udemy, Coursera, and YouTube have Tai Chi courses taught by experienced practitioners.\n\nMake sure to contact these places directly to get the most updated information regarding their schedules, fees, and other details.",
